{"tid":2434443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"禿鷹：警方執行國安法跟足法例精神　唯部分人從感情層面覺濫捕","createTime":"2021-03-05T14:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T04:26:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"32c59264960be9a113751de83dbfa65fb987e24f","tid":2434443,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"在北京出席全國兩會的全國政協委員、警務處前處長曾偉雄認為，本港警方執行《港區國安法》時，有跟足法律目標、法治精神，亦有保障到人權，執法過程雖然嚴厲，但是根據法例行事。 <br />\n<br />\n他表示，如果從感情層面，同情被補人士的人可能會覺得警方濫捕，但認為從執法角度，警方並無濫捕，強調確保國家安全是特區的責任，反問如果無警方嚴格執行《港區國安法》，如何履行有關責任。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381783&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=0f2e12cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381783</a>"},{"pid":"666b6d45f7367ecb179cc28363d24da709234a8c","tid":2434443,"uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"佢做唔到UN狗官好嬲好嬲"},{"pid":"8b109ba4499d5497973736360b5558c1bae293dd","tid":2434443,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c973c08918ee2e32d9b07c6d241203a8fb5e4f","tid":2434443,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:25:21.000Z","msg":"未處死你呢位戰犯 都係因為理性公平公義沒有顯示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fcb52f764354d3b27680b6b01ec41a3973a39a","tid":2434443,"uid":261524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"有幾撚仆街先可以講得出呢埋野"},{"pid":"823e753276a740d7eb54114deb043db68c4e7be9","tid":2434443,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuc